D) Join in freely since others are doing it too (Integrity: -3, Public Trust: -4, Sustainability: -4)
Question 9: A friend asks you to sign them in for attendance while they skip class.
A) Refuse and explain why attendance fraud is unfair to everyone (Integrity: +5, Public Trust: +5, Sustainability: +5)
B) Refuse but offer to take notes for them instead (Integrity: +4, Public Trust: +4, Sustainability: +3)
